_sText:
This is my second map ever made. Since this is very old one, I'm going to remake it straight away after I finish my other jailbreak map projects. 

This map contains a pool, an empty yard, medic, an armory and big cage. (And of course the hidden disco.)

The custom textures are made by Ryan.

Oh yeah, the custom sounds or textures are not packed inside the bsp file, since I didn't know about Pakrat when I made this
